quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,127,"aur jab ibrahim aur asmayl beeet allah ki bunyadain onche kar rahay they ( to dua kiye jatay they ke ) ae perwar-digaar, hum se yeh khidmat qubool farma. be shak to suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai"
  2,128,"ae perwar-digaar, hum ko apna farmanbardar banaye rakiyo. aur hamari aulaad mein se bhi aik giroh ko apna Mutee banaye rahev, aur ( perwar-digaar ) hamein tareeq ibadat bta aur hamaray haal par ( reham ke sath ) tavajja farma. be shak to tavajja frmane wala meharban hai"
  2,129,"ae perwar-digaar, un ( logon ) mein inhen mein se aik paighambar maboos kejio jo un ko teri ayatain parh parh kar sunaya kere aur kitaab aur danai sikhaya kere aur un ( ke dilon ) ko pak saafkiya kere. be shak to ghalib aur sahib hikmat hai"
  2,130,"aur ibrahim ke deen se kon ro gardani kar sakta hai, bajuz is ke jo nihayat nadaan ho. hum ne un ko duniya mein bhi munhtakhibkiya tha aur akhirat mein bhi woh ( zumrahٴ ) sulhaا mein se hon ge"
  2,131,jab un se un ke perwar-digaar ne farmaya ke islam le aao to unhon ne arz ki ke mein rab alaalmin ke agay sir itaat khham karta hon
  2,132,aur abrhim ne apne biton ko isi baat ki wasiyat ki aur Yaqoob ne bhi ( apne frzndon se yahi kaha ) ke beta khuda ne tumahray liye yahi deen pasand farmaya hai to marna hai to musalman hi marna
  2,133,"bhala jis waqt Yaqoob wafaat panay lagey to tum is waqt mojood they, jab unhon ne apne biton se poocha ke mere baad tum kis ki ibadat karo ge, to unhon ne kaha ke aap ke mabood aur aap ke baap dada ibrahim aur asmayl aur Ishaq ke mabood ki ibadat karen ge jo mabood yaktaa hai aur hum usi ke hukum bardaar hain"
  2,134,yeh jamaat guzar chuki. un ko unn ke aamaal ( ka badla miley ga ) aur tum ko tumhare aamaal ( ka ) aur jo amal woh karte they un ki prssh tum se nahi hogi
